(66, 10, 1, '', '2015-04-21 07:11:44', 63, 5810, 'bd44df6e499b92c09c46b5f72a4da983e1693c2a', '{"id":10,"asset_id":100,"title":"FAQs","alias":"faqs","introtext":"<h2>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS (FAQs)<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><b>WHERE CAN BESEATED BE FOUND?<\\/b><br \\/> Beseated is available on various platforms:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Official Website (www.thebeseated.com)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Website is Mobile responsive (any device)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>iOS Devices (Beseated)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Android Devices (Beseated)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><b>ARE PRICES THE SAME AS DIRECTLY BOOKING WITH VENUES OR SERVICE PROVIDERS?<\\/b><br \\/> Yes, Venues and Service Providers set prices on the Beseated Platforms, so they are identical as the prices offered by them directly.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN RESERVING THROUGH BESEATED PLATFORMS AND DIRECTLY RESERVING WITH THE VENUE AND\\/OR SERVICE PROVIDER?<\\/b><br \\/> When You Get Beseated, You Get Rewarded !!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>CAN I INVITE FRIENDS ?<\\/b><br \\/> Beseated is integrated with Facebook and your phone contacts, therefore allowing you to invite friends to attend a Venue with you, or Join You in one of our premium packages that are paid in advance and split between you and invited friends.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>HOW DO I CHANGE OR CANCEL A RESERVATION?<\\/b><br \\/> Cancellations should be made 24 hours prior to the date of the reservation or as specified in the terms of the Venue and\\/or Service Provider, in order to refund the deposit or amount paid.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT HAPPENS IF NO SHOWS OCCURS FOR A VENUE RESERVATION?<\\/b><br \\/> As per Venue Terms &amp; Policies, the deposit paid will not be refunded.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT HAPPENS IF NO SHOWS OCCURS FOR A SERVICE RESERVATION?<\\/b><br \\/> Depending on Service Provider Terms &amp; Policies, a penalty will be applied to the amount or full amount will be lost.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHY WAS MY RESERVATION CANCELLED?<\\/b><br \\/> The Venue or Service Provider can cancel reservations. In this case, the full amount or deposit paid will be FULLY REFUNDED. If you have further enquiries, please contact the Venue or Service Provider directly for clarifications.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>HOW AND WHERE CAN I USE MY LOYALTY POINTS?<\\/b><br \\/> When rewarded with Beseated loyalty points, you may use Loyalty Points to pay for some of the Venue deposits or Service amounts and the rest on your Credit Card depending on the accumulated points earned. For more information, See Rewards section.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>HOW CAN I SUBMIT RATINGS AND REVIEWS FOR VENUES AND SERVICE PROVIDERS?<\\/b><br \\/> After 24 hours of a completed reservation, once you use our Platform again, a ratings and review page will appear to fill in order to proceed using the app.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>CAN I RESERVE THROUGH THE WEBSITE AND FOLLOW UP ON MY APPLICATION OR THE OTHER WAY AROUND?<\\/b><br \\/> Yes, all platforms are connected to one server, as long as you use same sign-in details.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>DO I NEED PROOF OF MY RESERVATION WHEN ARRIVING TO THE VENUE?<\\/b><br \\/> No, proof of identity will only be required.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT IS YOUR POLICY ON INFORMATION SECURITY?<\\/b><br \\/> Please revert to our Privacy section.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT IF WE NEED TO ADD MORE PEOPLE TO OUR TABLE?<\\/b><br \\/> A request can be sent and the venue may accept or decline the request according to its status.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>CAN WE REQUEST A CUSTOMIZED PACKAGE?<\\/b><br \\/> Send us your request on the contact form in the Contact section, and we will try our best to help you with your needs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN A NORMAL QUEUE\\/WALK IN AND JOINING THE Q ON BESEATED?<\\/b><br \\/> Being on the Q in our platform gives you a better chance to get in when the venue is busy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>IF A SECURITY PERSONNEL IS CHOSEN, IS THERE A SPECIFIC TIME FOR THEM TO LEAVE?<\\/b><br \\/> Hours required are made directly on the Beseated platforms. You can ask the Personal Security for more hours, however, will not be rewarded with Loyalty Points.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>THE PERSON WHO MADE THE RESERVATION IS THE ONLY PERSON TO GET POINTS?<\\/b><br \\/> Yes, however when a package is reserved and the bill is split equally, the group will share equal points.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>If you have other enquiries, please see Contact section and fill the form with your query, and we will try to assist you as soon as we can.<\\/b><\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2015-04-21 07:11:44","created_by":"63","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2015-04-21 07:11:44","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ord