(102, 6, 1, '', '2015-08-24 14:12:52', 63, 5846, '173e9a3c61bbe5271639f68fcd041713633080a2', '{"id":6,"asset_id":"104","title":"Rewards","alias":"rewards","introtext":"<h2 style=\\"margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 50px;\\">Beseated Rewards System Terms and Conditions<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>It is the Beseated member\'s responsibility to read and understand the terms and conditions regarding Reward System, outlined below.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>Rules Concerning Beseated Rewards System<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Only Beseated registered members can participate in Rewards System and earn Loyalty Coins. Members earn Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0depending on the reservation amount and company policy, unless stated otherwise. Loyalty Points are awarded within one month of completing full payment.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Beseated reservations that do not originate on www.thebeseated.com may not be eligible for Loyalty Point awards. If a reservation is eligible to earn points, the points value associated with that reservation will be displayed on the reservation details and confirmation pages, as well as in the confirmation email.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>If a member needs to modify a reservation, the change should be made online at www.thebeseated.com or on the Beseated Application, twenty four (24) hours prior to the reservation time or as specified by the Venue or Service Provider - in order to ensure that any applicable Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0are awarded.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Beseated is not responsible for awarding Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0if a member or members are unable, for any reason, to make or honor an online reservation. Reasons a member may be prevented from making a reservation online include, but are not limited to:<br \\/> Technical difficulties<br \\/> Venue or Service Provider does not accept online reservations for party size requested<br \\/> Venue or Service Provider is closed<br \\/> Venue or Service Provider does not take reservations that far in advance<br \\/> Members will not receive any Loyalty Points when a reservation is canceled or the member(s) does not show up.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><b>Terms and Conditions<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Beseated reserves the right to terminate Loyalty Rewards, or to change these Terms and Conditions, regulations, or benefits of participation, in whole or in part, at any time with or without notice, even though changes may affect the number of Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0already accumulated. Beseated may also withdraw, limit, modify or cancel the number of Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0required for reward redemption or change the number or type of reward offered. Beseated will have final decision should any disputes occur over Loyalty Rewards or the awarding of Loyalty\\u00a0Coins.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Beseated reserves the right to terminate a member\'s Loyalty Rewards\' account and cancel accrued Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0if Beseated believes, in its sole discretion, that the member is abusing the Loyalty Rewards program, or is misrepresenting any information furnished to Beseated.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Any Beseated member who fails at any time to earn Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0for a period of twelve (12) months is subject to termination of his or her membership and forfeiture of all accrued Loyalty Coins. See above rule for more detail.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>If a member(s) is unable to honor a reservation and fails to cancel, Beseated will send the member an email stating that our records indicate there was a no-show. If a member\'s account accumulates four (4) no-show reservations within a twelve-month period, Beseated may cancel that member\'s account and cancel all accrued Loyalty\\u00a0Coins.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Should Beseated offer rewards from any of the partners, Beseated will not be responsible for any partner\'s participation in or withdrawal from Loyalty Rewards.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0earned by a member in two or more different accounts cannot be combined to redeem any award.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Members are solely responsible for any tax liability related to participation in Loyalty Rewards.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Inquiries regarding the Beseated Loyalty\\u00a0Coins\\u00a0assigned to a reservation must be submitted via email within 7 days after the reservation date in order to be considered for review by Beseated.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If you need further information or clarification please visit our FAQ section.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":"1","catid":"2","created":"2015-04-23 12:58:34","created_by":"63","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-08-24 14:12:52","modified_by":"63","checked_out":"63","checked_out_time":"2015-08-24 14:05:00","publish_up":"2015-04-23 12:58:34","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}",